-- MOVES-Guy Hill joins Sanditon Asset as senior investment director
-- 
-- Thu Nov 06, 2014 01:34PM EST
-- None



Nov 6 (Reuters) - London-based Sanditon Asset Management said it appointed Guy Hill senior investment director.

Hill joined this week from Helvea, where he headed the Swiss equities team in London, Sanditon said in a statement. He will work with Chris Rice in the European investment team.